		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GADDIEL &lt;/strong&gt;has entered into agreement with Sattva LLC to develop enterprise solutions for their health care operations in India.  The enterprise solution will address the core business requirement and interface the data with other peripheral non-core functions like Accounting, HR, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The top level requirements, modules of the application and phase-wise implementations are finalized.  Detailed requirement and phase-wise interfacing requirements are under analysis.&lt;/p&gt;
